        <mxCell id="scoreBox" value="&lt;b&gt;Compliance Summary (MCP Spec 2025-11-25)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&#xa;✔ Fully Implemented: Lifecycle, Protocol Versioning, JSON-RPC Strictness, RFC 9728 (.well-known), RFC 6750 (401/403 WWW-Authenticate), RFC 8707 (resource param), PKCE/State/Nonce (OAuth 2.1), Origin Validation, ping, logging/setLevel, Request Timeouts, Capability Honesty&lt;br/&gt;&#xa;⚠ Opt-in / Partial: Token Audience Validation (MCP_SERVER_RESOURCE_URI must be explicitly set in production)&lt;br/&gt;&#xa;✗ Optional Not Implemented: Cancellation, Progress, Tasks (experimental) — all MAY, no client depends on them&lt;br/&gt;&#xa;— N/A: Elicitation URL mode, Sampling tools/toolChoice (not part of this architecture)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#1a1a2e;fillColor=#eaf4fb;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;spacingBottom=8;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
